LADIES AND GENTLEMEN.

2:01:04.705 --> 2:01:07.190
HE WAS FINISHED.

2:01:07.225 --> 2:01:09.917
CASSIUS MARCELLUS CLAY JR.

2:01:09.952 --> 2:01:13.300
